          }
        },
        {
          "id": "el-1776637247929-19",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>Making changes to your site doesn't have to be frustrating. Focus your time on running your business and leave the website changes to us.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "text_color": "rgb(85, 85, 85)",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Open Sans",
            "typography_font_size": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 15
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "el-1776637247929-20",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>If your website doesn't load quickly, your audience is likely to navigate away. Loading speed must be one of the top priorities that you focus on.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "text_color": "rgb(85, 85, 85)",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Open Sans",
            "typography_font_size": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 15
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "el-1776637247929-21",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>We implement WordPress security best practices to help prevent any loss of business due to malicious activity and data breaches.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "text_color": "rgb(85, 85, 85)",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Open Sans",
            "typography_font_size": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 15
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "el-1776637247929-22",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>WordPress continually introduces updates to boost its security, and foregoing these can potentially open your website up to cyber attacks.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "text_color": "rgb(85, 85, 85)",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Open Sans",
            "typography_font_size": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 15
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "el-1776637247929-23",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>Backup your website to the cloud on a daily basis for added security and reliability. Easily recover from any incident with one-click restores.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "text_color": "rgb(85, 85, 85)",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Open Sans",
            "typography_font_size": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 15
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "el-1776637247929-24",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "text-editor",
          "settings": {
            "editor": "<p>Downtime can be costly for any online business. 24/7 website monitoring helps to quickly resolve any lapses in your site's uptime.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "text_color": "rgb(85, 85, 85)",
            "typography_typography": "custom",
            "typography_font_family": "Open Sans",
            "typography_font_size": {
              "unit": "px",
              "size": 15
            }
